<div>
<p xml:id="subtitle1" begin="35869166t" end="54637916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我老爸奋进人…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle2" begin="62979582t" end="86336250t" region="region0"><span style="style1">是一个万年老二的英雄</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle3" begin="96346250t" end="111361249t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我的儿子焦冻</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle4" begin="113446666t" end="135552082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">肩负着超越欧尔麦特的义务</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle5" begin="152235416t" end="187270416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">假如你跟第一英雄之间</span><br/><span style="style1">有任何关系的话</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle6" begin="191441250t" end="200200000t" region="region0"><span style="style1">那么…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle7" begin="209375832t" end="228561666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我就更得赢过你才行</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle8" begin="252335416t" end="287370416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我记忆中的母亲…一直在哭泣</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle9" begin="294877916t" end="320320000t" region="region0"><span style="style1">“你的左半边实在太丑陋了”</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle10" begin="331164166t" end="357023332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">她一边说一边把热水浇到我身上</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle11" begin="380797082t" end="408741666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">就算没有那个臭老爸的个性 我也…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle12" begin="412495416t" end="450032916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不对 就算不使用 我也能成为第一</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle13" begin="450867082t" end="471721249t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我要借此完全否定他</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle14" begin="486736249t" end="512178332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">总之 不管你是欧尔麦特的什么人</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle15" begin="519685832t" end="544710832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我都只会用右半边的力量超越你</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle16" begin="572655416t" end="599765832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">但是…我也绝对不可以输</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle17" begin="606439166t" end="633549582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">这也是为了回报那些</span><br/><span style="style1">曾经帮助过我的人们</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle18" begin="649398750t" end="663162500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我一定会赢过你</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle19" begin="822905416t" end="859608749t" region="region0"><span style="style1">片名：我的英雄学院</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle20" begin="1632464166t" end="1665830832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">但是…你想成为英雄不是吗？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle21" begin="1709207499t" end="1734232499t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你可以…当英雄的</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle22" begin="1760925832t" end="1770935832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不知道从何时起…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle23" begin="1776774999t" end="1798880416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我把这之后的记忆都忘了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle24" begin="1964045416t" end="1972804166t" region="region1"><span style="style1">（轰焦冻对战绿谷出久）</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle25" begin="1980311666t" end="2002834166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">四强赛的第一场比赛</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle26" begin="2007422082t" end="2043708332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">这两个人这次运动会的成绩</span><br/><span style="style1">也都优秀得不得了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle27" begin="2052467082t" end="2073738332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">绿谷</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle28" begin="2092089999t" end="2106270832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">他会先发动冰冻招式</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle29" begin="2113778332t" end="2157155000t" region="region0"><span style="style1">对战 轰！</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle30" begin="2165079582t" end="2195943750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">让他随意发挥那股力量的话</span><br/><span style="style1">会很危险</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle31" begin="2204285416t" end="2235983750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">场上可说是双雄并立 现在</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle32" begin="2240988750t" end="2254752500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">要在开始的一瞬间…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle33" begin="2259757500t" end="2281445832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">-开始！</span><br/><span style="style1">-发动攻势</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle34" begin="2299797500t" end="2312727082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">爆碎风</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle35" begin="2402400000t" end="2433264166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">-好冷</span><br/><span style="style1">-怎么光是风就这么冷？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle36" begin="2494992500t" end="2515012500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">果然不出我所料</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle37" begin="2533781250t" end="2553801250t" region="region0"><span style="style1">抱着牺牲觉悟的抵销战术</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle38" begin="2572152916t" end="2610524582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">绿谷成功化解了轰的冰冻攻击</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle39" begin="2611358750t" end="2653901250t" region="region0"><span style="style1">因为不清楚轰少年</span><br/><span style="style1">究竟会发动多大规模的攻势</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle40" begin="2654735416t" end="2687267916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">所以他舍弃了控制能力</span><br/><span style="style1">以百分之百的威力攻击</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle41" begin="2706453750t" end="2740237500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">要对付他的冰冻攻击</span><br/><span style="style1">的确就只能用这一招</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle42" begin="2748996250t" end="2757755000t" region="region0"><span style="style1">但是…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle43" begin="2773187082t" end="2801131666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">爆碎风</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle44" begin="2808639166t" end="2830327500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">绿谷再度化解了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle45" begin="2872452916t" end="2895392500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">轰同学的战斗都在瞬间结束</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle46" begin="2898312082t" end="2922085832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">能得知的情报太少了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle47" begin="2925422500t" end="2934598332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">情报…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle48" begin="2938769166t" end="2972135832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">必须在这场战斗中找到他的弱点才行</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle49" begin="2981728750t" end="3001748750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">在他背后的那道冰墙</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle50" begin="3004251250t" end="3029693332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">应该是为了不被我轰飞</span><br/><span style="style1">所采取的对策</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle51" begin="3034281250t" end="3045125416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">这么一来</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle52" begin="3049713332t" end="3064728332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">使用手指是正确的</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle53" begin="3072652916t" end="3098095000t" region="region0"><span style="style1">就算牺牲手臂</span><br/><span style="style1">使出百分之百威力的爆碎风</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle54" begin="3098929166t" end="3116863750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">他也很有可能应付得了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle55" begin="3138135000t" end="3150647500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">得快点看穿</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle56" begin="3158989166t" end="3184014166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">加快思考 找出他的弱点</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle57" begin="3195275416t" end="3221134582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">得在…剩下的六发察觉</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle58" begin="3237817916t" end="3249496250t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你这家伙</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle59" begin="3350013332t" end="3364611249t" region="region0"><span style="style1">还剩五次机会</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle60" begin="3403817082t" end="3415495416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">已经开始了啊</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle61" begin="3417580832t" end="3443439999t" region="region0"><span style="style1">切岛 恭喜你晋级四强赛</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle62" begin="3448027916t" end="3475138332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">谢谢 爆豪 下场就跟你打了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle63" begin="3475972499t" end="3493489999t" region="region0"><span style="style1">-请多指教</span><br/><span style="style1">-我会宰了你</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle64" begin="3510173332t" end="3535198332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">放马过来！话虽如此</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle65" begin="3536032499t" end="3573987082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你跟轰一样</span><br/><span style="style1">都会接二连三地使用大范围攻击</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle66" begin="3576489582t" end="3585665416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">轰一下打过来</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle67" begin="3589836249t" end="3611107499t" region="region0"><span style="style1">而且丝毫不给人喘息的空间</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle68" begin="3611941666t" end="3633629999t" region="region0"><span style="style1">才不是接二连三 少瞧不起人了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle69" begin="3651564582t" end="3679092082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">过度使用肌肉 肌肉纤维就会断裂</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle70" begin="3681177499t" end="3699529166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">一直跑 一样会气喘吁吁</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle71" begin="3715378332t" end="3744991249t" region="region0"><span style="style1">就算是我 释放的威力一样有极限</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle72" begin="3752498749t" end="3770850416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">所以我才会花心思 把战斗服设计成</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle73" begin="3771684582t" end="3810890416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">就算使用超过极限的爆炸</span><br/><span style="style1">也不会有任何风险</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle74" begin="3829659166t" end="3846342499t" region="region0"><span style="style1">个性也算是身体机能</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle75" begin="3853015832t" end="3886382499t" region="region0"><span style="style1">场上那两个家伙…应该也有某种极限</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle76" begin="3891804582t" end="3911407499t" region="region0"><span style="style1">仔细想想 的确是这样</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle77" begin="3917663749t" end="3942688749t" region="region0"><span style="style1">所以绿谷打算对秒杀对手的轰使出…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle78" begin="3953115832t" end="3967296666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">持久战是吗？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle79" begin="3973969999t" end="3993989999t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我会马上结束比赛</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle80" begin="4010256249t" end="4030276249t" region="region0"><span style="style1">爆碎风</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle81" begin="4054049999t" end="4074069999t" region="region0"><span style="style1">右手已经全毁了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle82" begin="4084079999t" end="4124537082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">轰 毫不畏惧绿谷的力量</span><br/><span style="style1">快速向他逼近</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle83" begin="4125371249t" end="4142054582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">可恶</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle84" begin="4253415832t" end="4266762499t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不行 太近了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle85" begin="4502414582t" end="4532861666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">跟刚才比起来 威力还要更强大</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle86" begin="4554132916t" end="4567062500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不希望我…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle87" begin="4571233332t" end="4582494582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">接近吗？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle88" begin="4620449166t" end="4640052082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不只是个性而已</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle89" begin="4648810832t" end="4676338332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">判断力 应变能力</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle90" begin="4677172500t" end="4688016666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">机动力</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle91" begin="4693438750t" end="4705534166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">他所有的能力</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle92" begin="4711790416t" end="4720549166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">都好强</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle93" begin="4754750000t" end="4779775000t" region="region0"><span style="style1">他根本已经比一般职业英雄都强了啊</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle94" begin="4781860416t" end="4813141666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">感觉真不愧是第二英雄的儿子呢</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle95" begin="4823985832t" end="4835664166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">什么嘛？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle96" begin="4836915416t" end="4864025832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">光顾着逃跑跟防守就全身是伤了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle97" begin="4907402500t" end="4918663750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">他在颤抖</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle98" begin="4932010416t" end="4949527916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">原来是这么回事…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle99" begin="4960372082t" end="4979140832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">可恶</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle100" begin="4986648332t" end="4997492500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">真是不好意思</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle101" begin="5002080416t" end="5016678332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不过绿谷 谢谢你</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle102" begin="5022100416t" end="5056718332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">托你的福 那家伙的脸色变难看了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle103" begin="5081743332t" end="5109270832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">就算没有那个臭老爸的个性 我也…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle104" begin="5124702916t" end="5133878750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不对…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle105" begin="5143888750t" end="5172250416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">就算不使用 我也能成为第一</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle106" begin="5173084582t" end="5196024166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我要借此完全否定他</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle107" begin="5212290416t" end="5240652082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">看你的双手</span><br/><span style="style1">应该已经无法战斗了吧？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle108" begin="5246491250t" end="5257752500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">该让比赛结束了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle109" begin="5281526250t" end="5304465832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">轰以压倒性之势 接连发动攻击</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle110" begin="5306551250t" end="5323234582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">他使出最后的冰冻攻击</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle111" begin="5359937916t" end="5374118750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你到底在看哪里？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle112" begin="5541786250t" end="5553464582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你这家伙…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle113" begin="5565560000t" end="5581409166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">竟然用已经受伤的手指…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle114" begin="5598926666t" end="5616444166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">为什么要拼成这样？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle115" begin="5631042082t" end="5643971666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你在发抖呢</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle116" begin="5649393750t" end="5663574582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">轰同学</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle117" begin="5676504166t" end="5704031666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">说穿了 个性也是身体机能的一部分</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle118" begin="5709036666t" end="5746574166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">就算是你</span><br/><span style="style1">对寒冷也是有忍耐极限的吧</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle119" begin="5757835416t" end="5775770000t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不过 其实这点</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle120" begin="5782443332t" end="5822066250t" region="region0"><span style="style1">只要你使用左半边的火焰力量</span><br/><span style="style1">不就能解决了吗？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle121" begin="5858352500t" end="5867528332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">大家…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle122" begin="5872116250t" end="5886297082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">都是认真应战</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle123" begin="5897558332t" end="5906317082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">赢得胜利</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle124" begin="5918829582t" end="5935512916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">往自己的目标进一步迈进</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle125" begin="5945105832t" end="5961789166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">为了成为第一名</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle126" begin="5990985000t" end="6013090416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你要只用一半的力量获胜</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle127" begin="6028105416t" end="6042286250t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你还没有…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle128" begin="6046874166t" end="6076904166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">伤我一分一毫 对我造成任何伤害</span></p>
