<p xml:id="subtitle269" begin="11084823750t" end="11104843750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">焦冻</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle270" begin="11122361250t" end="11145300832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你终于接受自己了吗？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle271" begin="11147386250t" end="11163652500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">就是要这样</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle272" begin="11171577082t" end="11189928750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你从现在起 踏上起点</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle273" begin="11198270416t" end="11222878332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">继承我的血脉 超越我吧！</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle274" begin="11227883332t" end="11258330416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我的野心将由你来实现</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle275" begin="11321310000t" end="11348420416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">奋进人先生突然激励起孩子了吗？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle276" begin="11354676666t" end="11365520832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">他这么溺爱孩子啊</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle277" begin="11394299582t" end="11405560832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">好厉害</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle278" begin="11412651250t" end="11428500416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你在笑什么？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle279" begin="11438927500t" end="11474379582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">不但伤痕累累 还身处于这种状况下</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle280" begin="11482721250t" end="11493982500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你根本疯了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle281" begin="11514419582t" end="11535690832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">后果会怎么样 我可不管</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle282" begin="11647469166t" end="11656227916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">午夜时分</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle283" begin="11659147500t" end="11676247916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">要是再这样下去</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle284" begin="11681252916t" end="11695850832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">他的身体会撑不住</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle285" begin="11749654582t" end="11762167082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">尽可能接近他</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle286" begin="11771760000t" end="11783855416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">竭尽全力</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle287" begin="11788860416t" end="11808880416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">有本事就使出全力来啊</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle288" begin="11873111250t" end="11882287082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">绿谷</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle289" begin="11921492916t" end="11932337082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">谢谢你</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle290" begin="12010748750t" end="12020758750t" region="region0"><span style="style1">等等…</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle291" begin="12030351666t" end="12044115416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">是怎样啦？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle292" begin="12052040000t" end="12065386666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">真的假的啊？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle293" begin="12069974582t" end="12083321250t" region="region0"><span style="style1">情况到底怎么样了？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle294" begin="12286857916t" end="12316887916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">虽然说威力并不是越大越好</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle295" begin="12328566250t" end="12341495832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">但还真惊人啊</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle296" begin="12346917916t" end="12363184166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">拆房子啊</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle297" begin="12365686666t" end="12386540832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">你的班级到底怎么搞的啊？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle298" begin="12389043332t" end="12422827082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">先前充分冷却的空气</span><br/><span style="style1">突然在瞬间被加热</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle299" begin="12423661250t" end="12435339582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">当然就膨胀了</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle300" begin="12439510416t" end="12460364582t" region="region0"><span style="style1">所以才会产生爆风吗？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle301" begin="12462032916t" end="12477882082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">温度到底多高啊？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle302" begin="12484555416t" end="12525012500t" region="region0"><span style="style1">什…什么都看不见</span><br/><span style="style1">比赛结果怎么样了？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle303" begin="12717705000t" end="12739810416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">绿…绿谷同学</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle304" begin="12742730000t" end="12752322916t" region="region0"><span style="style1">出界</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle305" begin="12801538750t" end="12833237082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">由轰同学 晋级准决赛</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle306" begin="12846166666t" end="12899553332t" region="region1"><span style="style1">剧名：轰焦冻 原点</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle307" begin="13800453332t" end="13814217082t" region="region0"><span style="style1">（下集预告）</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle308" begin="13815051249t" end="13845081249t" region="region0"><span style="style1">是 我是有幸担任</span><br/><span style="style1">下集预告解说的A班班长</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle309" begin="13847166666t" end="13870523332t" region="region0"><span style="style1">我叫饭田天哉</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle310" begin="13871357499t" end="13890960416t" region="region0"><span style="style1">跟之前的预告开场几乎一样</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle311" begin="13891794582t" end="13922241666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">绿谷同学</span><br/><span style="style1">我发誓 会连你的份一起加油</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle312" begin="13924327082t" end="13933085832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">挺进决赛的</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle313" begin="13935588332t" end="13957276666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">-饭田同学一定办得到</span><br/><span style="style1">-是啊</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle314" begin="13961447499t" end="13994814166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">都到这一步了 就要获胜</span><br/><span style="style1">跟哥哥报告这个好消息</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle315" begin="13996482499t" end="14016502499t" region="region0"><span style="style1">下集 《饭田同学 加油》</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle316" begin="14018170832t" end="14038190832t" region="region0"><span style="style1">喂 妈 哥怎么了？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle317" begin="14040693332t" end="14059044999t" region="region0"><span style="style1">天才哥哥究竟出了什么事？</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle318" begin="14063215832t" end="14077396666t" region="region0"><span style="style1">更向前迈进吧！</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle319" begin="14078230832t" end="14094914166t" region="region0"><span style="style1">超越极致！</span></p>
